<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index Lower </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, July 27 (Xinhua) -- The general price index at Tehran
Stock Exchange closed lower at 1570.64 points Monday, down 1.08
points from Sunday's finish.
</P>
<P>
A total of 192,892 shares worth over 543,691,000 rials
(about 98,850 U.S. dollars) exchanged hands in 234 turns for
122 applicants. The shares of 13 companies made gains while
those of eight others declined. 
</P>
