contribute to the start in 1999 of economic recovery. Some mental
and instrumental factors that have so far accumulated will allow
the Government a good start, albeit not a spectacular one, enough
to restore trust in the times to come," the Premier said.
</P>
<P>
He reckoned that the first positive effects on people and the
living standards in Romania would be felt at the end of 1999 and
the beginning of the year 2000. 
