million ringgit (46.527 million U.S. dollars) against Monday's
80.815 million shares valued at 136.984 million ringgit (33.168
million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The main board turnover rose to 113.230 million shares valued
at 187.941 million ringgit (45.504 million U.S. dollars) from
69.664 million shares worth 131.403 million ringgit (31.817
million U.S. dollars) Monday.
</P>
