million shares traded on the main board, industrial products 6.621
million shares, construction 10.580 million shares,
trading/services 37.805 million shares, infrastructure 1.132
million shares, finance 31.359 million shares, hotels 386,000
shares, properties 10.323 million shares, plantation 2.733 million
