from July 29 to 31 here.
</P>
<P>
The international community, besides watching the outcome of
the South Asian Association for Regional Cooperation (SAARC)
Summit in Colombo, will pay special attention to the meeting of
the prime ministers of India and Pakistan as it would be the first
high-level encounter between them after their nuclear tests in
May.
</P>
