<HEADLINE> Rio Group to Discuss Incorporation of Central America </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Ivett Franco Koroneos, an official from the Panamanian Foreign
Ministry, said the presidents from the Rio Group member countries
will focus on the peace in Central America and relations with
Europe.
</P>
<P>
She said the presidents of the group will also deal with issues
