relieve burdens on Chinese farmers in order to ensure their
enthusiasm for production and ensure this year's output target.
</P>
<P>
-- Vice-Premier and Head of the State Flood Control and Drought
Relief Headquarters Wen Jiabao yesterday urged Hubei and other
provinces along the Yangtze River to protect the embankments of
the Yangtze River, major cities and people's lives and properties.
</P>
<P>
He also asked yesterday the provinces to win a decisive victory
against the surging waters during his inspection tour of the
provinces.
</P>
<P>
"China Daily"
</P>
<P>
