emergency yesterday to meet the threat from the rising water of
the Yangtze River and called for top priority to be given to
flood-relief work.
</P>
<P>
Surging water in the Yangtze has passed the danger level in the
two provinces and meteorologists believe they may rise to record
highs in the next few days.
